RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

95-1728. State v. Algarin.

Erie County, No. E-94-029. Reported at 74 Ohio St.3d 1411, 655 N.E.2d 409. IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of the dismissal of this case for want of prosecution be, and hereby is, denied, effective November 3, 1995.
